&lt;h3 id=&quot;1-add-widget&quot;&gt;1. Add Widget&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;오른쪽 상단에서 Widget List 버튼(파란부분영역)을 클릭하면 Widget List Side Bar가 Slide 되어 나타난다.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:4000/images/works/20160906/image-1.png&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://localhost:4000/images/works/20160906/image-1.png&quot; alt=&quot;dashboard&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:4000/images/works/20160906/image-2.png&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://localhost:4000/images/works/20160906/image-2.png&quot; alt=&quot;dashboard&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;만들고자 하는 Widget을 드래그하여 원하는 위치에 놓을 수 있다.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:4000/images/works/20160906/image-3.png&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://localhost:4000/images/works/20160906/image-3.png&quot; alt=&quot;dashboard&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:4000/images/works/20160906/image-4.png&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://localhost:4000/images/works/20160906/image-4.png&quot; alt=&quot;dashboard&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:4000/images/works/20160906/image-5.png&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://localhost:4000/images/works/20160906/image-5.png&quot; alt=&quot;dashboard&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;2-resize-widget&quot;&gt;2. Resize Widget&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Widget 테두리 부분을 마우스로 잡고 드래그 하여 크기 조절이 가능하다.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:4000/images/works/20160906/image-6.png&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://localhost:4000/images/works/20160906/image-6.png&quot; alt=&quot;dashboard&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:4000/images/works/20160906/image-7.png&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://localhost:4000/images/works/20160906/image-7.png&quot; alt=&quot;dashboard&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:4000/images/works/20160906/image-8.png&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://localhost:4000/images/works/20160906/image-8.png&quot; alt=&quot;dashboard&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;3-configure-the-widget&quot;&gt;3. Configure the widget&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Widget의 오른쪽 상단 버튼(파란영역부분)을 클릭하여 Configuration 화면으로 이동 가능하다.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:4000/images/works/20160906/image-9.png&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://localhost:4000/images/works/20160906/image-9.png&quot; alt=&quot;dashboard&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:4000/images/works/20160906/image-10.png&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://localhost:4000/images/works/20160906/image-10.png&quot; alt=&quot;dashboard&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:4000/images/works/20160906/image-11.png&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://localhost:4000/images/works/20160906/image-11.png&quot; alt=&quot;dashboard&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Configuration 화면의 오른쪽(파란영역부분)에서 Widget Chart 검색 조건을 수정할 수 있다.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:4000/images/works/20160906/image-12.png&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://localhost:4000/images/works/20160906/image-12.png&quot; alt=&quot;dashboard&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Configuration 화면의 왼쪽(파란영역부분)에서 Widget Chart 검색 조건을 통하여 반영된 Chart 미리보기가 가능하다.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:4000/images/works/20160906/image-13.png&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://localhost:4000/images/works/20160906/image-13.png&quot; alt=&quot;dashboard&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;오른쪽 상단(파란영역부분)의 ‘Apply’ 버튼을 클릭하면 수정사항이 반영된다.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:4000/images/works/20160906/image-14.png&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://localhost:4000/images/works/20160906/image-14.png&quot; alt=&quot;dashboard&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;오른쪽 상단의 ‘뒤로가기’ 아이콘(파란부분영역)을 클릭하면 변경된 사항은 반영되지 않고 취소되어 Dashboard 화면으로 전환된다.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:4000/images/works/20160906/image-15.png&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://localhost:4000/images/works/20160906/image-15.png&quot; alt=&quot;dashboard&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;4-remove-widget&quot;&gt;4. Remove Widget&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Widget의 오른쪽 상단 버튼(파란영역부분)을 클릭하여 Widget을 삭제할 수 있다.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:4000/images/works/20160906/image-16.png&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://localhost:4000/images/works/20160906/image-16.png&quot; alt=&quot;dashboard&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:4000/images/works/20160906/image-17.png&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://localhost:4000/images/works/20160906/image-17.png&quot; alt=&quot;dashboard&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name></name></author><category term="A-Cubed" /><category term="html" /><category term="css" /><category term="guide" /><category term="dashboard" /><summary type="html">A-Cubed Dashboard &amp;amp; Widget 가이드 제공</summary></entry><entry><title type="html">(보류)Markup: A-Cubed Buttons</title><link href="http://localhost:4000/markup-acubed-buttons/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="(보류)Markup: A-Cubed Buttons" /><published>2015-06-01T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2015-06-01T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/markup-acubed-buttons</id><content type="html" xml:base="http://localhost:4000/markup-acubed-buttons/">&lt;p&gt;Bootstrap을 이용한 A-Cubed Buttons Design.
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;buttons&quot;&gt;Buttons&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Make any link standout more when applying the &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;.btn&lt;/code&gt; class.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;language-html highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;a&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;href=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;#&quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;btn_success&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;Success Button&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; class=&quot;btn&quot;&gt;Basic Button&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; class=&quot;btn&quot;&gt;Selected Button&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; class=&quot;btn&quot;&gt;OK Button&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; class=&quot;btn&quot;&gt;Cancel Button&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; class=&quot;btn&quot;&gt;Apply Button&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; class=&quot;btn btn_danger&quot;&gt;Delete Button&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; class=&quot;btn&quot;&gt;Primary Button&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; class=&quot;btn btn_success&quot;&gt;Success Button&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; class=&quot;btn btn_warning&quot;&gt;Warning Button&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; class=&quot;btn btn_danger&quot;&gt;Danger Button&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; class=&quot;btn btn_info&quot;&gt;Info Button&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;language-markdown highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;Primary Button Text&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;](&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;sx&quot;&gt;#link&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;{: .btn}
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;Success Button Text&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;](&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;sx&quot;&gt;#link&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;{: .btn .btn_success}
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;Warning Button Text&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;](&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;sx&quot;&gt;#link&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;{: .btn .btn_warning}
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;Danger Button Text&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;](&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;sx&quot;&gt;#link&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;{: .btn .btn_danger}
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;Info Button Text&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;](&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;sx&quot;&gt;#link&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;{: .btn .btn_info}
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

